<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> svasti śrī</hi> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> tirumakaḷ puṇarap pu<unclear>kaḷ</unclear>makaḷ viḷaṅka
<lb n="2"/>vikkirama<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>yamakaḷ poṟpuyat tiruppak kaṉakameruviṟ 
<lb n="3"/>kayal viḷaiyāṭa Irunilat torutaṉi veṇkuṭai niḻaṟṟa <unclear>Uya</unclear>
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ru maṇimuṭi taṉurimaiyiṟ cūṭi Ulaku potu niṅka Oru
<lb n="5" break="no"/>kolocci vañcimaṉṉarum vaṭapula ven=tarum Añci van=ti
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ṟaiñci Aṭimalar cūṭi maṉṉiya vira<hi rend="grantha">siṁhāsa</hi>nattu Ula
<lb n="7" break="no"/>kamuḻutuṭaiyāroṭum viṟṟirun=taruḷiy<supplied reason="lost">ā</supplied> māmutal mati<unclear>k</unclear>kula
<lb n="8" break="no"/>m viḷakkiya komutan komāṟapaṉmarāṉa <hi rend="grantha">tribhu</hi>vanaccakkara
<lb n="9" break="no"/>vattikaḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>parākkiramapāṇṭiyatevaṟki vāṇṭu<note n="111-1">The inscription is left unfinished.</note>
</p>

